			<td colspan="2" style="line-height: 110%; padding-top: 0"><span style="font-size:12px;">(Left; top in mobile) A spectral image cube of Martin Waldseemüller’s 1507 world map, the first map to identify \'America.\' <em>Library of Congress</em>. (Right; bottom) The \'Nicolay Copy\' of the Gettysburg Address. <em>Library of Congress</em>.</span></td>
		</tr>
