<p>These initiatives – which offer a number of possibilities for the team to continue its transatlantic, scholarly-scientific-institutional collaborations – promise to help to realize one of the overarching objectives of the spectral imaging team’s original NEH grant, the "Digital Humanities <em>Start-Up</em> Grant" (emphasis added).</p>

