<div class="doubleleft" style="max-width:auto;"><a href="/sites/default/files/spectral-imaging/glossary-key-terms-in-livingstones-manuscripts-1870-71/liv_013726_0001-article.jpg"><img alt="Pilkington-Jackson, \'Last Journey,\' 1929, detail. Copyright Angela Aliff. May not be reproduced without the express written consent of the National Trust for Scotland, on behalf of the Scottish National Memorial to David Livingstone Trust." class="media-image attr__typeof__foaf:Image img__fid__306 img__view_mode__media_original attr__format__media_original" src="/sites/default/files/spectral-imaging/glossary-key-terms-in-livingstones-manuscripts-1870-71/liv_013726_0001-article.jpg" style="height: 450px; margin-right: 10px" typeof="foaf:Image&quot;" /></a></div>

<div class="doubleright"><a href="/sites/default/files/spectral-imaging/glossary-key-terms-in-livingstones-manuscripts-1870-71/liv_013727_0001-article.jpg"><img alt="Pilkington-Jackson, \'Last Journey,\' 1929, detail. Copyright Angela Aliff. May not be reproduced without the express written consent of the National Trust for Scotland, on behalf of the Scottish National Memorial to David Livingstone Trust." class="media-image attr__typeof__foaf:Image img__fid__306 img__view_mode__media_original attr__format__media_original" src="/sites/default/files/spectral-imaging/glossary-key-terms-in-livingstones-manuscripts-1870-71/liv_013727_0001-article.jpg" style="height: 450px;" typeof="foaf:Image&quot;" /></a></div>
