			<td colspan="2" style="line-height: 110%; padding-top: 0"><span style="font-size:12px;">Images of two pages of Field Diary VII (Livingstone 1866f:[57], [121]). <em>Copyright David Livingstone Centre. <a href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc/3.0/" target="_blank">Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial 3.0 Unported</a></em>. The page at left (top in mobile) illustrates part of Livingstone\'s route, while the page at right (bottom) has a section in brown ink that discuss the transportation of Livingstone\'s letters by Arab travellers.</span></td>
