	<tbody>
		<tr>
			<td colspan="2" style="line-height: 110%; padding-top: 0"><span style="font-size:12px;">(Left; top in mobile) Chumah and (right; bottom) Susi. Illustrations from James E. Ritchie, <em>The Pictorial Edition of the Life and Discoveries of David Livingstone</em>, 2 vols (London and Edinburgh: A. Fullarton &amp; Co., 1876-1879), 2:65. <em>Copyright Adrian S. Wisnicki. <a href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc/3.0/" target="_blank">Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial 3.0 Unported</a></em>. These illustrations of Chumah and Susi resemble photos of the two men taken in England after Livingstone\'s death.</span></td>
