<p>The majority of pages held by the David Livingstone Centre – all of the first gathering (1870b, DLC shelfmark: 297a); and parts of the second gathering (1870h:XVII-XX, DLC shelfmark: 297d; and 1870j:LXII-LXIX, DLC shelfmark: 297e) – do not bear any sort of archival numbers. However, one or more unknown archivists have numbered the pages 1870b as follows:</p>

