<div class="doubleleft"><a href="/sites/default/files/in-his-own-words/the-final-field-diaries-general-overview/liv_000002_0038-article.jpg"><img alt="An image of a page of Field Diary II (Livingstone 1866a:[38]). Copyright David Livingstone Centre. Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial 3.0 Unported (https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc/3.0/)." class="media-image attr__typeof__foaf:Image img__fid__306 img__view_mode__media_original attr__format__media_original" src="/sites/default/files/in-his-own-words/the-final-field-diaries-general-overview/liv_000002_0038-article.jpg" style="height: 396px; margin-right: 10px" title="An image of a page of Field Diary II (Livingstone 1866a:[38]). Copyright David Livingstone Centre. Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial 3.0 Unported (https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc/3.0/)." typeof="foaf:Image&quot;" /></a></div>

