<div class="doubleleft"><a href="/sites/default/files/life-and-times/livingstones-medical-education/liv_013419_0001-article.jpg"><img alt="The large arteries of thorax and neck. Copyright Wellcome Library, London. Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International (https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/)." class="media-image attr__typeof__foaf:Image img__fid__306 img__view_mode__media_original attr__format__media_original" src="/sites/default/files/life-and-times/livingstones-medical-education/liv_013419_0001-article.jpg" style="height: 450px; margin-right: 10px" typeof="foaf:Image&quot;" /></a></div>

