<h4><strong>II. Document Header</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style="font-family: crimson text;"><a href="#TOP" title="Go to table of contents"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family: source sans pro;">Top</span></span> ⤴</a></span></h4>

