<h4><strong><span style="font-family:crimson text;">Journal Entries and Notes</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </strong><span style="font-family: crimson text;"><a href="#TOP" title="Go to table of contents"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family: source sans pro;">Top</span></span> ⤴</a></span></h4>

