<p>The two pages that follow in this copy-book, 1871f:CXXXII [v.1]-CXXXIII [v.1], consist of notes, so this line of text clearly serves to connect 1871f:CXXXI to 1871f:CXXXII [v.2], which comprises the first page of the second copy-book.</p>

